{"tid":1433804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我有說話想講比勇武聽","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:40:11.000Z","uid":283713,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b8655362ee1ecd29697101941d1fbc280ec44511","tid":1433804,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"係呢兩個月來，我屋企人一直保持中立，怎至都可以叫做藍<br />\n當然我亦都會一有時間去盡我本分同兩老講呢兩個月既事實，包括警察濫權濫捕暴力...送中後果，燈柱等等...<br />\n可惜我兩老一直覺得示威者搞到香港好亂，警察的確需要清埸<br />\n但自從北角事件後，兩老已經睇法唔同，認為若果冇勇武去北角保護就會變成元朗2.0，亦親眼睇清楚警察一次又一次同黑社會合作，兩老真係好多謝你地，但同時好擔心你地受傷害，為香港實在付出太多...眼淚就不自覺流<br />\n希望我地會有一日除口罩擁抱大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，北角街坊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武，多謝你地</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">答應我，不流血不受傷不被捕</span></span>"},{"pid":"a67d94395d38edb99eab7a6cfb32e8ccd4d5deac","tid":1433804,"uid":283713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"我愛勇武"},{"pid":"e0c78a90bb7a992b81aeb620ff454c353427d5fc","tid":1433804,"uid":217441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"要開始學識講多謝手足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121ceb4a96124e371472a45b0780ec96270fd5a3","tid":1433804,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a67d94395d38edb99eab7a6cfb32e8ccd4d5deac","tid":1433804,"uid":283713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"我愛勇武"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"支持絲打係前線搵男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fd66f9b9cd2de3e8d06fd858c78ebe691da377","tid":1433804,"uid":270871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG2R3KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k